MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 25b5d8c9d1b74819a26d9f124959de2e, type: 3}
  m_Name: WaveCatalog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  waves:
  - displayName: 第 01 波
    designerNote: Use the first wave to introduce the basic scavenger swarm and one fast wolf burst.
    spawnGroups:
    - enemyType: 1
      enemyCount: 5
      spawnInterval: 0.95
    - enemyType: 2
      enemyCount: 2
      spawnInterval: 0.55
  - displayName: 第 02 波
    designerNote: Introduce shield support and stealth pressure while still keeping the total count readable.
    spawnGroups:
    - enemyType: 1
      enemyCount: 4
      spawnInterval: 0.85
    - enemyType: 3
      enemyCount: 1
      spawnInterval: 1.1
    - enemyType: 6
      enemyCount: 2
      spawnInterval: 0.8
  - displayName: 第 03 波
    designerNote: Mix heavy armor, repair support and one death-split boss-style unit.
    spawnGroups:
    - enemyType: 5
      enemyCount: 2
      spawnInterval: 1
    - enemyType: 4
      enemyCount: 1
      spawnInterval: 1.15
    - enemyType: 7
      enemyCount: 1
      spawnInterval: 1.4
    - enemyType: 2
      enemyCount: 3
      spawnInterval: 0.5
